      "title": "<span id=\"#33409\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">furthermore</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adv.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>约1200年，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of further \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/further\">further</a>（副词）+ <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of more \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/more\">more</a>。中古英语中也有一个 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">farthermore</i>。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Furthermost</i>。</p>"
